00:00:10.870 --> 00:00:20.890
And let's say I have
a vector 1, 2.

00:00:20.890 --> 00:00:24.610
So my vector looks like this,
1, and then we go up 2.

00:00:24.610 --> 00:00:27.230
So my vector looks like this.

00:00:27.230 --> 00:00:29.110
Let me draw it.

00:00:29.110 --> 00:00:30.370
That is my vector.

