00:22:02.620 --> 00:22:04.850
We're going to get
a 2-by-2 matrix.

00:22:04.850 --> 00:22:09.680
We get 2 times minus 1 plus 1
times 0, so this is just going

00:22:09.680 --> 00:22:11.090
to be minus 2.

00:22:11.090 --> 00:22:16.790
And then here, you get 2 times
0 plus 1 times 1, so you're

00:22:16.790 --> 00:22:18.250
